<i>I'm happy as can be</i>

15
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:34,715
<i>Let‘s go walking you and me</i>

16
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:37,440
<i>Ready, set, come on, let's go</i>

17
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:42,674
<i>The foxes and the badgers, too</i>

18
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:46,594
<i>All come out to play</i>

19
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:50,070
<i>They all want to explore</i>

20
